  "caption": "\"The day is not far when India will be the hub of industrial manufacturing and the world will be looking towards it.\"\n\nPM Narendra Modi said this. And the numbers are proving him right.\n\n99% of mobile phones sold in India are now manufactured domestically. Mobile imports dropped 85%. Manufacturing jobs surged 200% between 2022 and 2024. India is targeting $300 billion in electronics production.\n\nThis is not distant future talk. This is happening now.\n\nAt Cu Circuits, we are proud to be part of this story. Every PCB we fabricate in Chennai is one more component that does not need to be imported. Every 3D printed prototype we deliver helps an Indian hardware startup move faster.\n\nThe manufacturing revolution is not coming. It is here.\n\nWhat are you building? We would love to fabricate it.\n\n#MakeInIndia #IndiaManufacturing #ElectronicsManufacturing #PCBManufacturing #CuCircuits #HardwareStartup #AtmanirbharBharat",
  "strategy": {"format": "quote_data_mashup", "visual_approach": "large quote with India map SVG background and stat cards"},
